<https://ofn.gov.cz/dcat-ap-cz-hvd#dcat:DatasetShape/-7dbb2fe4> a sh:PropertyShape;
    sh:description "The HVD IR is a quality improvement of existing datasets. The intention is that HVD datasets are publicly and open accessible. Therefore a Distribution is expected to be present. (Article 3.1) This section provides more information how this strong recommendation is implemented."@en;
